description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Community Mental Health Nurse – Band 6.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;There is an exciting opportunity to work with people with dementia, their family and carers -&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for Band 6 Community Mental Health Nurse’s to join our Dementia and Older Peoples Mental Health Service in West Sussex covering the Arun, Adur and Worthing area. Our vision is to provide outstanding care and treatment; the people that we employ are at the heart of making this vision a reality. If you&#39;ve got the passion, the belief, the drive and the talent to help us achieve our vision then we want to hear from you!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The role of this post is to actively engage those requiring an increased level of support with the aim of keeping people within their home and maintaining their wellbeing and independence as far as possible. We are looking for individuals who are dynamic, compassionate, good communicators and who are able to demonstrate a holistic and person-centred approach to their work.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Intensive Support operates an 8am – 7pm shift pattern, with a 1-hour break, 10-hour shift system Monday to Fridays, and 9am – 5pm with a half an hour, at weekends and bank holidays. There may be on occasions a need to change this shift pattern to 9-5pm 7 days a week at short notice to meet any changes that may occur in the service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Our team have a very friendly, experienced MDT, and a strong, supportive leadership group who place a real importance on staff wellbeing and in development. We are proud to be a service that encourages everyone to be the best that they can be and make the most of their careers whatever their background.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post offers a Golden Hello, or a Relocation package up to a maximum of £2000. (pro rata applies and subject to terms and conditions. Please see attached Protocol document).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sandra O&#39;Brien - Team Leader - Tel: 07768711304&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jo Livermore - Team Leader- Tel: 07909256455&lt;/p&gt;
